OL,3,CHollywood star Douglas Fairbanks
OL,4,CJunior's belongings put up for auction
OL,6,F"A lot of these things believe it or
OL,7,Fnot have been under my bed for 20 odd
OL,8,Fyears," says Nick Weston.
OL,10,F"Some things in a shoebox. Quite
OL,11,Fliterally!"
OL,13,FIt's not often that items belonging to
OL,14,Fa Hollywood megastar come up for
OL,15,Fauction, but, in the case of Douglas
OL,16,FFairbanks Junior, that's exactly
OL,17,Fwhat's happening at a Kent auction
OL,18,Fhouse.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
