PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776867068
OL,3,CHollywood star Douglas Fairbanks
OL,4,CJunior's belongings put up for auction
OL,6,FHis grandson, Nick - from Tunbridge
OL,7,FWells - has made the decision to part
OL,8,Fwith some extraordinary items he
OL,9,Finherited from his famous relative.
OL,11,FFairbanks Jr became a movie legend in
OL,12,Fthe golden age of Hollywood.
OL,14,FHis daughter, Daphne, moved to the UK
OL,15,Fin 1948, got married and raised four
OL,16,Fchildren. Among them was Nick.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776867068
OL,3,CHollywood star Douglas Fairbanks
OL,4,CJunior's belongings put up for auction
OL,6,F"We were very lucky, lots of lovely
OL,7,Ffamily holidays - Florida, New York.
OL,8,FSo when you're a youngster, that's all
OL,9,Fyou're thinking about, how lucky we
OL,10,Fare," Nick told ITV Meridian.
OL,12,F"But as we got older we saw him
OL,13,Fprobably two or three times a year and
OL,14,Fhe was very engaging, very
OL,15,Fcharismatic, as you can imagine."
OL,17,FA Cartier clasp, reflecting the movie
OL,18,Fstar's glittering career and
OL,19,Flifestyle, is among the treasure trove
OL,20,Fof items that Nick has put up for
OL,21,Fauction.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
