OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776867068
OL,3,CHollywood star Douglas Fairbanks
OL,4,CJunior's belongings put up for auction
OL,6,FA rare celluloid with a handwritten
OL,7,Fdedication from family friend, Walt
OL,8,FDisney, is also among the collection.
OL,10,FNick added: "We all got a print or a
OL,11,Fsigned copy when we were born, so
OL,12,Fthat's how we got hold of those."
OL,14,FNick says it's time for this unique
OL,15,Fcollection to see the light of day.
OL,17,FThe auction is being held at Hansons'
OL,18,Fsaleroom in Penshurst.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
